 Disconnect the central lead and disconnect the ground lead.\",\"comments\":null},{\"status\":\"1\",\"name\":\"Police the area for detonator cord remnants. unused\\/damaged charges etc. And store then in the explosives remnant box and lock.\",\"comments\":null},{\"status\":\"1\",\"name\":\"Store all unused detonators in the detonator carving case and lock.\",\"comments\":null}],\"status\":\"signed\",\"creator_id\":20,\"sign_status\":\"fully_signed\",\"created_at\":\"2025-10-14T12:20:46.000000Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2025-10-15T11:10:22.000000Z\",\"external_sign_status\":\"pending\"}', 'http://10.205.59.106/checklists/checklists/4/approve', '10.205.59.117', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/141.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', 25, '2025-10-15 11:10:22', '2025-10-15 11:10:22');
